data.description: Welcome home to this one owner lovingly cared for 2005 Cheyenne model. A spacious 2,783 sq ft, 3 bedroom, 2 & 1/2 bath & 3 car garage. Foyer leads to home office with built-in file cabinets & bookshelves. A large sitting & dining room allow for family gatherings and gorgeous views of the Catalina Mountains. Open concept kitchen with engineered stone countertops and wet bar features hickory cabinets with black GE appliances and a stainless steel refrigerator. Split bedroom floorplan. Family room has custom-built oak entertainment center with space to accommodate a large screen T.V. Owner's suite has upgraded wood flooring plus dual walk-in closets with built-ins for added storage space. Front patio is a great place to watch the sunrise. Full length covered patio features gas line for BBQ.
